node.accessibility_caption: Photo by O L I V I A in Chicago, Illinois with @walgreens. May be an image of food.

node.text:
honey, we’re nuts about @walgreens // #ad 

welcome to round two of olivia recommends snacks from #walgreens! here’s my second favorite (sorry, but still obsessed with sriracha ranch) flavor of nice! cashews: honey roasted. you all know i completely lose any sense of routine or adult behavior (saving money?? eating regular meals?? never heard of it) in the summer, but fortunately these are…
a. available in-store, online, or via pick-up at any walgreens
b. affordable compared to national brands like planters
c. easy to eat—i like to toss mine in greek yogurt with some berries in the morning for extra energy.

let me know in the comments which you’d choose between sriracha ranch or honey roasted—there might be something in it for one of you 😉
